Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.42,0:00:06.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,與步行俠的對決後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:10.16,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,「倖存者」的各位都暫時癱倒在床上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:13.51,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不只是身體上遭受了創傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:16.23,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,內心也或多或少有心事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:22.75,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,人類太閒的時候就會不自主地胡思亂想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.68,0:00:25.75,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,想那些因匆忙而忘記的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:28.28,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,想那些刻意不願想起的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.59,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,都會再度占據腦海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:35.11,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,人類這東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:42.52,renleiyongzhe note1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(785.2,856)}{\fade(500,500)\pos(690.8,841.6)}冒險者還沒能拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.78,0:00:50.79,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我們接下來要去什麼樣的城市  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:54.52,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是好久沒去的迷宮都市
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:57.93,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你還記得阿爾卡斯叔叔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:00.02,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,他摸過我的腦袋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:01.39,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,又能見到他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:07.45,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:18.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,爸爸和媽媽都愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:19.94,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.83,0:01:25.86,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,幫大忙了  阿爾卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:28.54,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,為…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:20.47,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:25.44,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,「黏水關」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:29.33,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,最低等級的冒險者首先要從這裡開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:32.91,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,從今天起我也是冒險者了吧  阿爾卡斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:33.72,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:37.48,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,還有成為冒險者之後就不要叫我「先生」了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.53,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,冒險者間沒有上下之分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:41.19,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,聽好了  尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:45.24,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,冒險者之間就是要信任彼此相互協助…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:46.35,renleiyongzhe text up,,0,0,0,,啊  它在吃草
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:47.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:51.48,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,太大意的話小心被偷襲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:53.65,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我知道啦  阿爾卡斯先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.62,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這就叫大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:13.42,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,雖然我成為冒險者是為了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:16.35,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但也有想過如果那時自己有力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:20.25,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,說不定能和父親母親一起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.30,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,加入「武藝百般」時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.68,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,阿爾卡斯給了我一把短劍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.17,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,最讓我開心的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:40.51,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,他是考慮到我的資質才選給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:45.90,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這都是些陳年舊事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:47.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我的過去已經被吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.98,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,並作為現在的我的一部分了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:54.42,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,即便如此  我也沒有覺得後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:57.03,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,要是那時候那樣做的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.44,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,要是那時候這樣做的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:02.83,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,如果我給了阿爾卡斯不同的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.96,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我現在會不會還在「武藝百般」中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.42,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,如果那時我沒逃走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:13.03,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,會不會和父親母親一起死去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.50,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,如果那時…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:46.00,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,小阿加特？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.29,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,小阿加特為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:58.32,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不過只看頭頂就能認出來真不愧是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:03.60,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,麻煩了啊  看起來雨不會那麼快停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:05.08,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,真巧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:07.75,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我還在頭疼怎麼把傘還給你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:11.63,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這樣說的話你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:24.20,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,說起來  我還沒問過你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:25.25,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:28.63,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我只是個喜歡偶像的野狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:30.83,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:32.32,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:35.33,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我也只是個偶像的阿加特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.12,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那天也下著雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:40.31,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:45.09,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,看到野狗先生在雨中都不打傘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.87,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,下意識地就跟你聊起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:51.27,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但知道野狗先生也有自己的家真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.65,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,說起來  之前我們事務所的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:58.49,renleiyongzhe text up,,0,0,0,,打斷一下  你要在這種狀態聊很久嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.06,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,給你帶來麻煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:04.36,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不  說不上是麻煩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:06.69,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那就再聊一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:08.26,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.19,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,說不定就是因為有那天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:15.99,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我才得到了救贖也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:18.18,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你剛剛說了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:19.48,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.94,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,難道說  野狗先生是那種
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:24.22,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不時會有幻聽的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:25.36,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,煩捏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:32.62,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:35.07,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,還要這樣站著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:38.38,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,至雨止時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:56.38,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,已經可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:03.46,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,殺死納爾迦瓦醫生的人是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:07.71,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:09.97,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:11.98,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.32,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我贏囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:17.30,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我就知道你要的是納爾迦瓦醫生的繼承權
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.93,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:23.06,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,哪有人為了打賭斷三根肋骨的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你根本不懂啊  醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:28.97,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,如果我輸了的話又有三根要斷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:31.97,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,贏了的話你那三根能恢復得快點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:38.63,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那種事怎麼可能發生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:40.66,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這醫生腦子沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:45.78,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,治療是個好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:49.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,雖然很微不足道  但能幫到其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:53.47,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,在治療時不用想多餘的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:55.98,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不可思議的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:59.31,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,步行俠納爾迦瓦先生如此劣跡斑斑應當憎惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:04.46,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,現在的我卻無法憎恨他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:08.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,像是繼承他的道路似的模仿他的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.99,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是在追悼嗎  亦或是自我滿足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:16.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不  這兩者或許是同一種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.02,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:19.80,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:23.55,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:31.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:40.42,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:43.12,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好幾次我反覆從夢中驚醒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,以些許的救贖為餌食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.85,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,今日的我仍舊被苦惱折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:03.24,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:07.79,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,人生真是如此殘酷之物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:10.31,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,昨日已過而今日猶存
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:13.29,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,向目光可及處前進
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.93,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,人類是否真的無法得到回報呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:23.19,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,賭博這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:26.11,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,在沒有贏錢的直覺的時候就不該下注
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.69,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,雖然我提不起興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.31,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但為了找回日常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:32.27,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這些天我都在模仿著從前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:35.91,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,多麼奢侈的發言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:38.80,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我對這樣的生活沒什麼不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:45.52,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,現在  應該也沒有人會騙我或拖我的後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:47.35,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,生活順心如意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:49.83,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我還能有什麼不滿的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:50.84,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:54.22,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:57.90,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,勝負相當收支均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:00.88,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:03.20,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這樣太無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.19,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.16,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,卡蘭有沒有嚐過這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:20.52,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:22.32,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:24.18,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:26.84,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,大伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:31.63,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,大伙過得還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.25,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,馬馬虎虎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:41.35,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你還在堅持啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:46.89,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,約好了不干涉他人的隱私的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:50.84,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:57.82,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,雖然步行俠事件中有讓人傷心的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.24,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但最後也達到了計劃中的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:03.81,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我們必須接受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.32,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這恰如其分的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:12.04,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但是  現在大家之間卻有了層無形的障壁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:13.54,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,無論是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:16.82,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,看起來似乎都在與某種東西鬥爭著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:32.58,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,倖存者三條款  其一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:35.65,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,絕不干涉他人的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:39.02,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你說什麼都沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:43.49,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你這種人真這麼想就是白費口舌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:44.86,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:47.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:52.05,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,居然在這麼危險的地方行醫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:00.59,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,怎麼看都需要我的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:02.76,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,就當我是保鏢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:05.89,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:09.44,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.60,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:14.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這不是新一期的月刊利莫里亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:17.10,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,奧莉薇婭還是老樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.54,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,讓我看看寫了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:21.91,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,遊走於迷宮都市有意思的怪人前100名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:23.91,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,大家已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:29.65,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,已經吃過早飯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:33.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,呃  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:36.16,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我一整晚都在打包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:38.27,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,已經在雷德先生那吃過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:40.47,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我抽兩口就當早餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:46.04,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊  那我先去吃點東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:58.84,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,難道大家都已經釋懷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:01.53,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:06.02,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我以前的隊長  卡里歐斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:10.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那個我曾經宣誓效忠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.74,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,卻背叛了我  拋棄了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:16.92,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,還把我所有的東西都偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:19.97,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,雖說他欺騙了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:23.42,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但在「白鷺」的日子我其實過得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:28.46,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,只是  卡里歐斯偷走了我族群的寶物「龍王寶珠」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:30.27,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這件事是決不能被原諒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:32.87,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我從沒有忘記這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:37.26,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,小妹妹你是虎人族東西得輕拿輕放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:40.15,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,怎麼會  我什麼都沒做過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.40,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,無心之舉確實沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:45.07,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,可裝傻可不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.45,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但是  我真的沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:50.29,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,雖說你看上去是剛從鄉下來不久的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:54.45,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但在這「迷宮都市」可不能就這麼算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:58.35,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你是要用半價1萬底拿買下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:00.10,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:01.88,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:04.98,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,要確認下這女孩的爪痕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:13.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,卡蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:19.92,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,大家怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.94,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,聽說大伙在準備「夏眠祭」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:24.58,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,想著過去瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:26.58,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,「夏眠祭」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.59,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,寫作在夏天中入眠  所以叫「夏眠祭」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:34.41,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,聽說在這個季節魔物的活動也會弱化哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.32,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,能吃到好東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:40.19,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那應該是有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:42.44,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那可真讓人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:48.26,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那麼耀眼的光芒有將一日也會消失得無影無蹤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.83,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,消失的話  是好事還是壞事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:53.46,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:55.86,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,只是覺得當下越是重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.29,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,相對的  過去就會漸行漸遠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:02.76,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,即便如此  珍重仍留存下來的東西那就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:07.81,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,如果是的話  我想只留下我喜歡的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:14.63,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,高傲的龍人族有著一項使命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:19.28,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那就是協助能成為勇者的人類拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:24.51,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我是龍人族椿氏族族長的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:26.21,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,卡蘭椿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:29.00,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,寄宿了火龍之加護
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:31.06,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,一名高傲的龍戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:34.43,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:37.09,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不好了不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:39.80,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,奧莉薇婭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:43.93,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不好了  是號外哦  號外號外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:47.76,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是月刊利莫里亞的特別號外哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:49.36,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你在吵什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:51.60,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀  不得了了各位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:53.21,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,真的是個大新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.70,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,看起來確實很不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.04,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不得了得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:58.73,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,到底是什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:01.05,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,現在怎麼還能這麼平靜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:03.95,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,情緒不再高漲點我可不說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:07.96,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,什什什什麼  到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:09.81,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不錯哦  不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:12.54,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我很討厭這種煽動行為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:16.44,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,其實啊  居然有這麼一回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:17.02,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:22.04,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,特報  發現了傳說中的暗黑魔人復活徵兆…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:23.72,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,的傳聞？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:26.48,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我說  別在我之前爆出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.77,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不是你自己把這篇報道撒得周圍都是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:30.71,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,又是假新聞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:35.65,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,老是說點沒邊的東西  以後沒人信你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:40.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但——是呢  這次我的信源是槓槓的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.02,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,什麼  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:44.59,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不愧是絆  眼光就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:45.69,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:47.23,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你別當真了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:51.76,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,如果我說「白色假面」也牽扯其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:52.97,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:55.21,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這點倒還不能確認
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:58.47,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,如果我說搞清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:01.95,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,流通「幻王寶珠」的黑市所在地了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:03.64,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你搞清楚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:04.85,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,現在還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:09.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,雖然我現在還沒搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.36,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但把那些可疑的點連接起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:14.26,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,並寫出吊人胃口的新聞就是我的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:16.72,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,牽強附會的東西可不算新聞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:18.08,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:20.05,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,都說無風不起浪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:22.75,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,如果沒有風就讓八卦雜誌掀起浪花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:26.72,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,從剛才開始你就在說自己在編大話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:28.18,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,編大話？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.82,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不不  麻煩你說這是浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:31.99,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是浪漫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:33.50,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是浪漫哦  絆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.89,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,聽起來真令人雀躍啊  浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:37.82,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,「龍王寶珠」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.40,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,也會流進你說的那個黑市嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:42.78,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,卡蘭小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:49.70,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,說實在  我確實不該執著於卡里歐斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:54.52,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但是  我不知道我該怎麼辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:57.62,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,雖然跟大家一起的日子很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:00.72,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但我也感覺到自己在對什麼事情視而不見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.23,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:09.60,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,有著放不下的東西  那麼抓住就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:14.10,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,只是  你這次可不是一個人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:15.15,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.26,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,像步行俠那次一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:19.26,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我們一起行動就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:22.41,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,尼克…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:25.09,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,有什麼問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:27.12,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我們是「倖存者」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:30.92,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,無論我們要跟誰做對手  都一定要活著回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:34.17,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,納爾迦瓦和「白色假面」之間的關聯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.17,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,某種程度上是事先就能看出的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:38.92,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,而關於更深層的關聯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:40.92,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我也經常有聽說一些流言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:44.28,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,壞人的背後會牽扯到好人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.82,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,惡的背後連接的是更大的邪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:49.22,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,壞人們背後的背後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:51.74,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,找到最深處的那個頭頭  然後打飛他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:54.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,事情開始有趣起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.40,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你完完全全上了她的賊船了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:57.97,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那我們就幹這一筆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:18:58.39,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:00.53,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,都說到這份上了定得懲奸除惡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:00.87,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:03.00,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,尼克  我也想一起幹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:05.80,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,全員一致  讓我們一起打倒傳說中的魔神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.00,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,加了個油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.34,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:10.50,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,算了  就這樣吧
