Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:19.77,op-j,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}信じ貫く勇気を　持たず　未来へ行けない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:25.92,op-j,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:25.92,op-j,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}僕らは　試され続けている
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:31.17,op-j,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:31.17,op-j,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}さあ　ここから　取り戻せ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:36.13,op-j,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:36.13,op-j,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}疑いに霞んだ　本当の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:43.02,op-j,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}
