Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:32.29,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}暈染地平線的晨曦的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:37.87,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:37.87,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}過去與如今完全耳目一新
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:44.98,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:44.98,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}乞求著什麼  想與誰一同前行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:50.54,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:50.54,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}在夢的盡頭  我終於心知肚明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:56.60,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:56.60,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}「只有絕望才知道希望」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:20:03.12,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:20:03.12,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}懷抱譏諷般的世間天理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:09.28,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:09.28,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}曾暗暗發誓「不會再有下次」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:14.30,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:14.30,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}然而卻吶喊著「但再來一次」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:19.77,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:19.77,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}沒有堅信到底的勇氣  無法邁向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:25.92,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:25.92,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}我們  接連不斷地受到考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:31.17,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:31.17,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}來吧  從現在開始盡數取回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:36.13,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:36.13,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}蒙上疑慮的真正的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:43.02,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:43.02,op-c,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100,100)}以「絆」之名  Glorious World
